@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant "Model (joblib)" as Model
participant "RFM Data (CSV)" as RFM

User -> Frontend: Enter customer_id & submit
Frontend -> Backend: POST /predict-loyalty {customer_id}
Backend -> Model: load model if not cached
Backend -> RFM: load rfm_features.csv
Backend -> Model: predict_proba(X)
Model --> Backend: probability
Backend --> Frontend: JSON {loyalty_score, loyal}
Frontend --> User: Display result

@enduml
